    "created_at": "2015-07-23T01:25:10Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-23T01:25:10Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The reason I ask about `grpc_secure_channel_create` -> `grpc_channel_create` isn't aesthetics, but because @a11r said we have to present the secure option as the default.\n\nBTW he also said the insecure option should be designed so that a user that selects it learns what is needed for him to switch to secure (except, obviously, \"how to get myself a certificate\").\n"
  },
